column1: Baby Barnaby's////My favorite dish on the menu is the Green Eggs. If you love eggs
column4: and cheese YOU NEED TO GET THIS. It is creamy
column6: melt in your mouth amazingness!!! This dish is served with chicken apple sausage which is good but too sweet (IMO) for me so I usually substitute it with a side of bacon. This plate also comes with crisp breakfast potatoes and they are soooooo delicious and addicting- it's seriously the best part of the meal.
